# A grouped list of configuration mappings.
#
# Format:
# \[GROUP\]
# FILE_OR_DIRECTORY
# create DIRECTORY
#
# Groups can be enabled by listing them in 'used-groups' file.
#
# To install your configs: 'make install-configs'
# See: 'package-groups' for managing apps

